{"Traces":[{"CenterLatitude":30.280059,"CenterLongitude":120.161693,"ZoomLevel":7,"Lines":[{"Markers":[{"Id":"6fd20ea17c7248bba079ab5d0f0c6e95","Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州"},{"Id":"013dd35fcbfb43798239014fb952de6e","Latitude":28.864049,"Longitude":121.151535,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN331082","Title":"临海"},{"Id":"3d3897bcd1c94b5990b948b238a3631b","Latitude":34.347436,"Longitude":108.946306,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":true,"RegionId":"CN6101","Title":"西安"}]}],"Markers":[{"Latitude":30.280059,"Longitude":120.161693,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3301","Title":"杭州 (出生地)","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"6fd20ea17c7248bba079ab5d0f0c6e95\");'><span id='6fd20ea17c7248bba079ab5d0f0c6e95_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=815&endYear=836')\">815-836年</a>，0-21岁</div><div id='6fd20ea17c7248bba079ab5d0f0c6e95' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=815&endYear=815')\">815年</a>，约生于本年。本表所列年岁为虚拟数，非实数。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=816&endYear=834')\">816-834年</a>，在故乡钱塘家居。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=835&endYear=835')\">835年</a>，在杭州。秋,郑巢拜谒姚合，与之游宴，郑巢有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>秋日陪姚郎中登郡中南亭。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">秋日陪姚郎中登郡中南亭（唐·郑巢）<br />　　五言律诗　押侵韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->云水生寒色，高亭发远心。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->雁来疏角韵，槐落减秋阴。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->隔石尝茶坐，当山抱瑟吟。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->谁知潇洒意，不似有朝簪。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=836&endYear=836')\">836年</a>，在杭州。秋,郑巢拜谒姚合，与之游宴，郑巢有诗《》、《》<span class='label'>作品：</span>和姚郎中题凝公院。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">和姚郎中题凝公院（唐·郑巢）<br />　　五言律诗　押先韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->后房寒竹连，白昼坐冥然。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->片衲何山至，空堂几夜禅。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->叶侵经上字，冰结砚中泉。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->雪夕谁同话，悬灯古像前。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=836&endYear=836')\">836年</a>，冬,姚合罢郡游越,郑巢有《》。\n游历天台山、剡溪等地,作诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>送姚合郎中罢郡游越。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">送姚郎中罢郡游越（唐·郑巢）<br />　　五言律诗　押尤韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->逍遥方罢郡，高兴接东瓯。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->几处行杉径，何时宿石楼。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->湘声穿古窦，华影在空舟。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->惆怅云门路，无因得从游。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":28.864049,"Longitude":121.151535,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN331082","Title":"临海","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"013dd35fcbfb43798239014fb952de6e\");'><span id='013dd35fcbfb43798239014fb952de6e_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=853&endYear=853')\">853年</a>，38岁</div><div id='013dd35fcbfb43798239014fb952de6e' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=853&endYear=853')\">853年</a>，在台州，刺史李肇幕府。<span class='label'>作品：</span>泊灵溪馆；瀑布寺贞上人院。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.347436,"Longitude":108.946306,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN6101","Title":"西安","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"3d3897bcd1c94b5990b948b238a3631b\");'><span id='3d3897bcd1c94b5990b948b238a3631b_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=854&endYear=855')\">854-855年</a>，39-40岁</div><div id='3d3897bcd1c94b5990b948b238a3631b' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=854&endYear=854')\">854年</a>，滞留京师，李肇出塞，有诗送。<span class='label'>作品：</span>送灵溪李侍郎。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">送灵溪李侍郎（唐·郑巢）<br />　　五言律诗　押文韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->貂裘离阙下，初佐汉元勋。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->河偃流澌叠，沙晴远树分。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->牛羊下暮霭，鼓角调寒云。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->中夕萧关宿，边声不可闻。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=855&endYear=855')\">855年</a>，滞留京师，有诗送边使。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">送边使（唐·郑巢）<br />　　五言律诗　押冬韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->关河度几重，边色上离容。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->灞水方为别，沙场又入冬。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->曙雕回大旆，夕雪没前峰。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->汉使多长策，须令远国从。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /></div>"}],"Title":"郑巢 <span class='inlineComment2'>(815-855)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：梁超然著《 三书斋文存 第2卷 古代文学研究（2）》、曹方林《姚合年谱（摘要）》、竺岳兵著.《唐诗之路唐代诗人行迹考》　录入整理：龚红林</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 3, 115.0489205, 31.6057425, 7)\">0-40岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">杭州</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">临海</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">西安</a></p>"}]}